Company Profile
Sector: Energy
Industry: Oil, Gas & Coal
Sub-Industry: Exploration & Production
Seadrill UK Ltd. provides offshore deepwater drilling equipment and platforms. The Company markets its services to oil and gas exploration and production companies around the world.




